      "date": "2019-02-13 05:41:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Gu, note that you need to request reviewers for your own patches,\n > and chase them when they don't respond instead of letting a patch\n > sit for weeks.\n > \n > You can use:\n > \n > $ ./contrib/scripts/get_maintainer.pl contrib/lbuild/lbuild\n > Minh Diep <mdiep@whamcloud.com> (reviewer:Lustre Build System,\n > commit_signer:4/9=44%,authored:3/9=33%,added_lines:19/49=39%,\n > removed_lines:27/37=73%)\n > Nathaniel Clark <nclark@whamcloud.com> (commit_signer:8/9=89%,\n > authored:5/9=56%,added_lines:29/49=59%,removed_lines:9/37=24%)\n > \n > to see a list of possible reviewers.  It isn't perfect, but at\n > least useful.\n\nHi Andreas,\nGot it, thanks for your suggestions. \nIt's my fault, as this issue is fixed by LU-11720, I closed the ticket, but forgot to abandon this patch.",
